message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR. The paper deals with natural language processing tasks such as question generation and uses deep learning models such as BiLSTM and Transformer. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), as these sub-categories also deal with deep learning and natural language processing.
